  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study to determine if HC2 HPV testing in the anal canal can detect high-risk HPV
      and whether this aids in identifying individuals are risk for anal cancer or precancerous
      lesions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
